## On Future

### 11.
```limn
wil = now + cho
```
**Future = present + choice**

> The future is simply the present moment plus the choices you make within it. Add choice to now, get tomorrow.

---

### 12.
```limn
fut = pos^unk
```
**Future = possibility at unknown intensity**

> The future is possibility at an unknowable intensity level. Could be intense, could be mild—you can't measure what hasn't happened.

---

### 13.
```limn
fer@wil > fer@was
```
**Fear-of-future > fear-of-past**

> Fear directed toward the future is always stronger than fear directed at the past. What might happen terrifies more than what did.

---

### 14.
```limn
wil\fer = hop
```
**Future minus fear = hope**

> Remove fear from your future and hope remains. Hope is the future freed from anxiety.

---

### 15.
```limn
you*tim = bec
```
**You interfering with time = becoming**

> You and time interacting create becoming. You're not static in time—you interfere with it, producing transformation.

